, as it boasts a 9.63% yield at</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1308949556/image_1308949556.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741684-ztr-play-forward-growth-utilities-high-yielding-cef", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 13:55:04"}, {"id": "4741669", "title": "Intel Rehashed: What Went Wrong? Maybe The Better Question Is, 'What Didn't?'", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Silicon Processor Chip\" data-id=\"1484082303\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FinkAvenue</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The announcement that Pat